title: SEE | Macan, Cayenne, Panamera - Here are the 5 fastest new Porsche cars you can buy
text:
Porsche is one of the most prestigious manufacturers in the motoring world.

The automaker's racing heritage stretches all the way from their conception on 25 April 1931 in Stuttgart, Germany to the innovative all-electric Porsche Taycan of today.

Powerful examples

We still have a while before the Taycan gets to South Africa, so let’s look at the fastest Porsche models you can get your hands on.

WATCH | All you need to know about the 2019 Porsche Macan Turbo

The guys from AutoAdvisor put together this cool list from the almighty 500kW Cayenne Turbo S E-hybrid Coupe to the agile 911 Turbo S, these are some of the fastest Porsche cars currently on the market.
